發一百粒彈</span>"},{"pid":"f80d5455816b43ff4569919759f6c87b330ac566","tid":1485211,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係金鍾既人可唔可以唔好咁自私 <br />\n早啲返屋企唔得 係都要踩死線 出哂防暴個啲先叫有做野？<br />\n個個都要擔驚受怕咁睇撚住你地 坐係到唔知做乜撚 次撚次都係咁 出左防暴 聽日個焦點又轉移左 可唔可以比返日個焦點係和理非到 今日咁多人出黎淋雨既努力 可唔可以唔好因為坐多個幾十分鍾而白費 求下你地啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"02a832edcf94f3bab0df69473254546154ae9329","tid":1485211,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"不割隻 不分化"},{"pid":"dfb71015bdb22b5be36ed696ec9052b5f754ad96","tid":1485211,"uid":34274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:44:58.000Z","msg":"喂 講還講又想借啲依分化兩派？"},{"pid":"bb861ba3ef51dc9d4001cb40bfb7cdeec9fa7df1","tid":1485211,"uid":199907,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"擺明唔係啦有一班明明可以走既,係都要留係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明係自己破壞共識<br />\n屈尻我地割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識玩既就一早走哂啦,仲會咁多人係到?"},{"pid":"3466ffcfc6e8ae24af391a96b2660c9737a2f140","tid":1485211,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"不割 但好多愚勇同花生友 希望作為前線手足要考慮埋自己安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9949cbff720713f9b3a3fc837f2bb90b3d33af46","tid":1485211,"uid":237388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:46:34.000Z","msg":"老老實實，其實好多真&bull;前線都識做，8點幾都開始走，依家留果啲似係業餘多過真&bull;前線"},{"pid":"da824cd376a0af906fcd9baec5a3e83ca2c372f7","tid":1485211,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"現場決定，我哋呢班冷氣軍師都係唔好講咁多喇"},{"pid":"42c1a836a08996bd8ea0ab0e8a6a49ce65ccf9fa","tid":1485211,"uid":199907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dfb71015bdb22b5be36ed696ec9052b5f754ad96","tid":1485211,"uid":34274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":